# A free text natural language description of the capability statement from a consumer's perspective. Typically, this is used when the capability statement describes a desired rather than an actual solution, for example as a formal expression of requirements as part of an RFP.
#: CapabilityStatement.description
msgid "Le rôle de gestionnaire incarné par un système, gère et stocke le cercle de soins,
donne accès aux informations en cas de consultation."
msgstr "The manager role embodied by a system manages and stores the care circle,
grants access to information in case of consultation."

# A representation of the meaning of the code in the system, following the rules of the system.
